Package: GeoDist
Type: Package
Title: Constrained distance calculation and associated geotools
Version: 0.1.0.8000
Author: Sébastien Rochette
Maintainer: Sébastien Rochette <sebastienrochettefr@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows the calculation of distances that are
    constrained by frontiers, islands, mountains, ... These distances are then
    implemented in classical geotools like kriging with a modified version of geoR
    functions.
Depends: R (>= 3.0), geoR
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    gstat,
    igraph,
    magrittr,
    methods,
    parallel,
    raster,
    readr,
    rgdal,
    rlang,
    snow,
    sp
Suggests:
